send

  • send(plr: MBCPlayer | MBCPlayer[], callback?: (plr: MBCPlayer, resp: ModalResponse) => void, onCancel?: (plr: MBCPlayer) => void, onTimeout?: (plr: MBCPlayer) => void): void

  • Overrides Form.send

    • Defined in src/classes/GUI/Form/ModalForm.ts:176

    Sends this modal form to a player or array of players

    example
    new ModalForm({
     components: {
       title: 'Example Modal Form',
       icon: 'textures/items/stick',
       components: [
         {
           id: 'sliderId',
           component: new Slider({
             label: 'Example Slider',
             minVal: 10,
             maxVal: 200,
           }),
         },
         {
           id: 'textboxId',
           component: new TextBox({
             label: 'Example Text Field',
             placeholder: 'Example Placeholder Text',
           }),
         },
       ]
     }
    }).send(player, (plr, resp) => {
     plr.sendMessage(Debug.format(resp));
     if (resp.sliderId > 100) plr.sendMessage('Slider value is over 100');
    }, (plr) => {
     plr.sendMessage('Closed modal form via cancelation');
    }, (plr) => {
     plr.sendMessage('Modal form timed out, likely due to having an existing ui open upon request');
    });

    Parameters

    • plr: MBCPlayer | MBCPlayer[]

      The player(s) to send this form to

    • Optional callback: (plr: MBCPlayer, resp: ModalResponse) => void

      A callback that is called when a valid response is received

        • (plr: MBCPlayer, resp: ModalResponse): void

        • Parameters

          • plr: MBCPlayer
          • resp: ModalResponse

          Returns void

    • Optional onCancel: (plr: MBCPlayer) => void

      A callback that is called when the form is closed

        • (plr: MBCPlayer): void

        • Parameters

          • plr: MBCPlayer

          Returns void

    • Optional onTimeout: (plr: MBCPlayer) => void

      A callback that is called when the form times out

        • (plr: MBCPlayer): void

        • Parameters

          • plr: MBCPlayer

          Returns void

    Returns void
